{"tid":2257322,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友大我十年，佢係我第一個女朋友，昨日分手。","createTime":"2020-10-25T05:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T10:15:49.000Z","uid":382247,"like":2,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ac981b74c76a5a5851e196a2b57bd396575a769d","tid":2257322,"uid":382247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:15:10.000Z","msg":"如題。背景:<br />\n打機網上識，拍左差唔多一年。我今年18佢28。女朋友樣靚身材正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，小弟現時讀緊I大，女朋友做緊物業管理。大部分時間同居，雙方家長都冇意見同埋見過家長。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日吵，因爲俾佢捉到我抄女同學牌。我自問我自己份人未夠定，先前已經因爲打機同第二條女太close吵過一次。宜家想複合。各位巴/絲打覺得應該放佢走定係挽留? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#第一次出post"},{"pid":"b7aed50ee613a557ae4777958c6895c0c048d5ec","tid":2257322,"uid":74278,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:17:17.000Z","msg":"你未試下cool下睇下點<br />\n個人夠唔夠定呢D野真係好撚死<br />\n同埋差十年呢<br />\n個價值觀同世界觀真係差好遠<br />\n所以...試下先囉<br />\n我覺得冇壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n青春就係任性既本錢"},{"pid":"ab236d1f43cadef251d095d541eb822bf18e82a5","tid":2257322,"uid":149833,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:22:06.000Z","msg":"試過一次又整多單<br />\n自己都話未夠定就放人走啦<br />\n女人青春有限，過多兩年就30"},{"pid":"425796b8e45927e5c809506271c852249ab41702","tid":2257322,"uid":319247,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:24:21.000Z","msg":"點識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefd7862463467ce2ca6c037ebb9015873a7bc2d","tid":2257322,"uid":20454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:28:06.000Z","msg":"放過人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed64ba949ff7f96d505f3201477e99a43d8b1a3f","tid":2257322,"uid":140726,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0